      <p>Por exemplo, veja Robert Nozick, <em>Anarchy, State, and Utopia</em> (New York: Basic Books, 1974), p. 169. <a href="#fnref:34" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
    <li id="fn:35" role="doc-endnote">
      <p>Veja os dados de Angus Maddison sobre o produto interno bruto per capita histórico, disponível em sua <a href="http://www.ggdc.net/maddison/Maddison.htm">página</a>. Veja também Angus Maddison, <em>Contours of the World Economy, 1–2030 AD: Essays in Macroeconomic History</em> (New York: Oxford University Press, 2003). <a href="#fnref:35" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
    <li id="fn:36" role="doc-endnote">
      <p>Rawls, <em>Theory of Justice</em>, p. 80. <a href="#fnref:36" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
    <li id="fn:37" role="doc-endnote">
      <p>Por exemplo, veja John Tomasi, <em>Free Market Fairness</em> (Princeton, NJ: Princeton University Press, 2012). <a href="#fnref:37" class="reversefootnote" role="doc-backlink">&#8617;</a></p>
    </li>
  </ol>
